    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Heat</strong> a large, wide-based pan with a matching lid (preferably non-stick) with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> vegetable oil over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> hot, add the carrot, celery and onion and cook, covered, for 4-6 min or until softened slightly</p>",
